long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
DOMark is a simple to use, fun and quirky way to organize your bookmarks.

From shopping, to paying bills, to learning and relaxing, so much of what we do happens online. With lots going on, it’s easy to get lost and lose track of what we were meant to be doing. When your tabs are stacking up and you’re starting to feel lost, DOMark can help you stay focused. DOMark prioritizes your most frequent online stops into action focused categories so you can quick go, do, and keep track of what needs to get done.

Do more with your bookmarks.

Features:
👟Quickly add new bookmarks to categories
👍 Stay on track by checking off what’s been done
🗄️ Auto categories to help you quickly sort and organize 
🤪 Light-hearted, easy to use design makes every to do list fun
